I have for sale a USA Tactical AR-15 made in Statesville, NC. 
It has a 16" Stainless Heavy Bull Barrel;
Competition Timney Trigger installed;
Magpul CTR stock, and magpul flip up sights;
SightMark Ultrashot QD (Quick Detach) optic;
Picatinny rail on top and bottom;
Vertical foregrip and three mode flash light installed (strobe, high, low);
Will include 3 (GI) magazines, and have more magazines I will sell separately if interested.

I bought the rifle new, and I have only fired a few magazines of american eagle ammunition through this rifle. It has been cleaned regularly. 

I am asking $1600 for this rifle obo.
